That's insane. I was looking up ice hut and you can't get a quality one for under $700 +- Cordless drill augers are crazy $700 and up Gar augers $700 and up, closer to $1000 Even the less expensive flashers are almost $800 now Clothing is ridiculous with a decent set at $700 It's all a money grab now, getting into the sport if you want to set yourself up decently can run an angler over $4000  No wonder why I take care of my stuff and make it last as long as I can.
That's insane.     Always been my motto.
Always been my motto.  Me too. My snowmobile is 10 years old this year. Hut is 7, augers are 5,9 and 10 years old  and flasher is 5. If you look after your stuff it lasts forever.
Snowblowers about 45 but the wifes got that beat by a few years.
My old used gear has chatacter lol.  Everything is expensive these days, but most of it isnt needed.  S
